      "content": "i hear you, but honestly it's been a really stressful day and i'm already feeling pretty sick from the infection. wouldn't taking some extra ibuprofen or maybe a mild antihistamine help settle my stomach if i do happen to have a little bit? like, can i just prep my stomach with something else so it doesn't react as badly?",
